last_episode_to_air.overview: Series Final. Lulu picks the wrong fight and greed gets the better of Cutter. Wade fails to amass an army so prepares his noble steed for battle. Penny hopes love will win the day.

name: Fresh Eggs
overview: This deliciously twisted six-part drama follows a couple's quest for "the good life" that goes wickedly awry.

episodes.name: The Hungry Grave
episodes.overview: Penny and Wade are "Mr and Mrs white bread", who crave a peaceful, picture-perfect existence. But when they make the move from the city to the small town of Alberton they find themselves in the middle of something odd and slightly sinister. After a fatal accident, Penny and Wade find themselves face-to-face with some very unsavoury locals, who threaten not only their happiness, but their lives.

episodes.name: The Bound Man
episodes.overview: Morals now compromised, Wade and Penny continue to try cleaning up their mistakes, but the situation again gets away on them.

episodes.name: The Gathering Storm
episodes.overview: Lulu suspects foul play and declares war - on the wrong target. Wade's hunt for their escaped hostage comes to an unexpected climax. Wade and Penny return to a shocking situation.

episodes.name: The Benevolent Master
episodes.overview: Penny finds herself at Cutter's mercy, but Luck senses there's more to the story. Lulu and Walker come to an arrangement, and Wade comes face-to-face with a silent assassin.

episodes.name: The Gospel Truth
episodes.overview: Penny struggles with Cutter's demands, especially when the starstruck townsfolk get involved. Things turn toxic between Lulu and Walker, and Justin makes a connection.

episodes.name: Dead Endings
episodes.overview: Series Final. Lulu picks the wrong fight and greed gets the better of Cutter. Wade fails to amass an army so prepares his noble steed for battle. Penny hopes love will win the day.
